00:24:08,350 --> 00:24:11,450
"Renown Detective of Gourmet Tour Solves the Case!"

418
00:24:11,450 --> 00:24:13,150
I'm sure we'll get high viewer rating!

419
00:24:14,750 --> 00:24:15,850
Yayoi?

